<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>성인 소득 데이터 분석 리포트</title>
<style>
  :root { --bg:#ffffff; --fg:#1a1a2e; --muted:#5c6370; --line:#e3e6ec;
          --accent:#3457d5; --ok:#0a8f4f; --no:#c02942; --card:#f7f9fc; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { margin:0; padding:2.5rem 1rem; background:var(--bg); color:var(--fg);
         font-family:-apple-system,"Apple SD Gothic Neo","Malgun Gothic",sans-serif;
         line-height:1.6; }
  .wrap { max-width:920px; margin:0 auto; }
  h1 { font-size:1.7rem; margin:0 0 .25rem; }
  h2 { font-size:1.2rem; margin:2.2rem 0 .8rem; padding-bottom:.4rem;
       border-bottom:2px solid var(--line); }
  .sub { color:var(--muted); font-size:.9rem; margin-bottom:1.5rem; }
  .grid { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:1rem; }
  .card { flex:1 1 180px; background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line);
          border-radius:10px; padding:1rem 1.2rem; }
  .card .k { color:var(--muted); font-size:.82rem; }
  .card .v { font-size:1.5rem; font-weight:700; margin-top:.2rem; }
  table { border-collapse:collapse; width:100%; font-size:.92rem; }
  th, td { text-align:left; padding:.55rem .7rem; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); }
  th { color:var(--muted); font-weight:600; }
  .tag { display:inline-block; padding:.15rem .6rem; border-radius:999px;
         font-size:.8rem; font-weight:600; }
  .tag.ok { background:rgba(10,143,79,.12); color:var(--ok); }
  .tag.no { background:rgba(192,41,66,.12); color:var(--no); }
  .test { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px;
          padding:1rem 1.2rem; margin-bottom:1rem; }
  .test .stat { color:var(--muted); font-size:.88rem; margin:.3rem 0 .5rem; }
  .test .msg { font-size:.92rem; }
  img { max-width:100%; border:1px solid var(--line); border-radius:10px; }
  .note { color:var(--muted); font-size:.85rem; }
  code { background:var(--card); padding:.1rem .35rem; border-radius:5px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="wrap">

  <h1>성인 소득 데이터 분석 리포트</h1>
  <div class="sub">생성 시각: {{ generated_at }} · 작성자: 광주캠퍼스 4반 길다인</div>

  <h2>0. 데이터 정제 요약</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card"><div class="k">원본 행 수</div><div class="v">{{ "{:,}".format(clean.n_before) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">정제 후 행 수</div><div class="v">{{ "{:,}".format(clean.n_after) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">결측 제거</div><div class="v">{{ "{:,}".format(clean.n_missing_dropped) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">중복 제거</div><div class="v">{{ "{:,}".format(clean.n_dup_dropped) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">고소득(&gt;50K) 비율</div><div class="v">{{ "%.1f%%"|format(clean.pos_rate * 100) }}</div></div>
  </div>

  <h2>1. 탐색적 분석 (EDA)</h2>
  <img src="{{ eda_img }}" alt="EDA 2x2 대시보드">

  <h2>2. 통계 가설 검정 (CDA)</h2>

  <div class="test">
    <strong>① t검정 — 소득집단 간 평균 연령 차이</strong>
    {% if ttest.significant %}<span class="tag ok">유의미</span>{% else %}<span class="tag no">비유의</span>{% endif %}
    <div class="stat">고소득 평균 {{ "%.1f"|format(ttest.mean_a) }}세 (n={{ "{:,}".format(ttest.n_a) }}) ·
      저소득 평균 {{ "%.1f"|format(ttest.mean_b) }}세 (n={{ "{:,}".format(ttest.n_b) }}) ·
      t={{ "%.4f"|format(ttest.t) }} · p={{ "%.4g"|format(ttest.p) }}</div>
    <div class="msg">{{ ttest.msg }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="test">
    <strong>② 카이제곱 — 성별과 소득의 연관성</strong>
    {% if chi2.significant %}<span class="tag ok">연관 있음</span>{% else %}<span class="tag no">독립</span>{% endif %}
    <div class="stat">chi2={{ "%.2f"|format(chi2.chi2) }} · dof={{ chi2.dof }} · p={{ "%.4g"|format(chi2.p) }}</div>
    <div class="msg">{{ chi2.msg }}</div>
  </div>

  <div class="test">
    <strong>③ ANOVA — 직군(workclass)별 근로시간 차이</strong>
    {% if anova.significant %}<span class="tag ok">유의미</span>{% else %}<span class="tag no">비유의</span>{% endif %}
    <div class="stat">F={{ "%.2f"|format(anova.f) }} · 그룹수={{ anova.k_groups }} · p={{ "%.4g"|format(anova.p) }}</div>
    <div class="msg">{{ anova.msg }}</div>
  </div>

  <h2>3. 소득 예측 모델 (KNN 분류)</h2>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card"><div class="k">정확도</div><div class="v">{{ "%.3f"|format(metrics.accuracy) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">고소득 정밀도</div><div class="v">{{ "%.3f"|format(metrics.precision_pos) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">고소득 재현율</div><div class="v">{{ "%.3f"|format(metrics.recall_pos) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">고소득 F1</div><div class="v">{{ "%.3f"|format(metrics.f1_pos) }}</div></div>
    <div class="card"><div class="k">Macro F1</div><div class="v">{{ "%.3f"|format(metrics.f1_macro) }}</div></div>
  </div>
  <p class="note" style="margin-top:1rem">혼동행렬 (행=실제, 열=예측, 0=&le;50K / 1=&gt;50K):
    [[{{ metrics.confusion[0][0] }}, {{ metrics.confusion[0][1] }}],
     [{{ metrics.confusion[1][0] }}, {{ metrics.confusion[1][1] }}]] ·
    학습 {{ "{:,}".format(metrics.n_train) }} / 평가 {{ "{:,}".format(metrics.n_test) }} ·
    재로딩 검증 {% if metrics.reload_ok %}OK{% else %}실패{% endif %}</p>
  <p class="note">{{ metrics.msg }}</p>
  <p class="note">피처 — 수치형: <code>{{ features.numeric|join(", ") }}</code> ·
    범주형: <code>{{ features.categorical|join(", ") }}</code></p>

  <h2>4. 학력별 고소득률 상위 10</h2>
  <table>
    <thead><tr><th>학력(education)</th><th>고소득(&gt;50K) 비율</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
    {% for row in edu_top %}
      <tr><td>{{ row.education }}</td><td>{{ "%.1f%%"|format(row.income_rate * 100) }}</td></tr>
    {% endfor %}
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p class="note" style="margin-top:1rem">인터랙티브 대시보드: <code>{{ plotly_file }}</code> (outputs/ 폴더에서 열람)</p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
